rows.label: qst200603_0010
rows.name: ...Hey, are we sure this is the place?

rows.label: qst200603_0020
rows.name:
Well, according to the soldier's
info, it should be around here...

rows.label: qst200603_0030
rows.name:
But will a demon beast really
appear in a place like this?

rows.label: qst200603_0040
rows.name: Don't ask me, I don't know...

rows.label: qst200603_0050
rows.name:
If someone saw it, then
something must be here, right?

rows.label: qst200603_0060
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?!

rows.label: qst200603_0070
rows.name: Something's coming out, mo.

rows.label: qst200603_0080
rows.name: Is that... the demon beast?

rows.label: qst200603_0090
rows.name: ...It's huge.

rows.label: qst200603_0100
rows.name:
...Even for a demon beast,
isn't that a bit too big?

rows.label: qst200603_0110
rows.name: It's incredible, mo...

rows.label: qst200603_0120
rows.name: Kubira.

rows.label: qst200603_0130
rows.name: Wait a moment.

rows.label: qst200603_0140
rows.name: Are you the demon beast?

rows.label: qst200603_0150
rows.name:
Hmph, to look down upon me... There is
a limit to not knowing one's place.

rows.label: qst200603_0160
rows.name: ...Well, so be it.

rows.label: qst200603_0170
rows.name:
It cannot be helped that you lack manners.
I shall grant you a special audience.

rows.label: qst200603_0180
rows.name:
Hey, are you an idiot? Going
off on your own like that.

rows.label: qst200603_0190
rows.name:
That's right, there's no way
we can beat that thing.

rows.label: qst200603_0200
rows.name: Can you hear me, demon beast?

rows.label: qst200603_0210
rows.name:
I am the king of a country
called Rigideria.

rows.label: qst200603_0220
rows.name:
It is already clear that you are
the one who destroyed my kingdom.

rows.label: qst200603_0230
rows.name:
As king, I must avenge my
sunken country and my people.

rows.label: qst200603_0240
rows.name:
If you are a being worthy
of the name demon beast...

rows.label: qst200603_0250
rows.name:
Then show me the power that destroyed
a kingdom, and wield it before me!

rows.label: qst200603_0260
rows.name:
What are you doing,
provoking it, Kubira?

rows.label: qst200603_0270
rows.name:
...Besides, can that demon
beast even understand words?

rows.label: qst200603_0280
rows.name:
What is it, demon beast... Do you
say you have no will to fight me?

rows.label: qst200603_0290
rows.name: ...Then, how about this?

rows.label: qst200603_0300
rows.name: Mo mo! What is he doing, mo?

rows.label: qst200603_0310
rows.name:
Ho... You beast, it seems you
are finally willing to fight.

rows.label: qst200603_0320
rows.name:
"Willing to fight," my
foot! You idiot, Kubira!

rows.label: qst200603_0330
rows.name: Now you've really made it mad!

rows.label: qst200603_0340
rows.name: Why did you provoke it?

rows.label: qst200603_0350
rows.name: What are you saying?

rows.label: qst200603_0360
rows.name:
Did we not come to this remote
place to defeat this demon beast?

rows.label: qst200603_0370
rows.name:
So what if we did? Why make it angry?
There's a way to fight, you know.

rows.label: qst200603_0380
rows.name: Good grief...

rows.label: qst200603_0390
rows.name:
To flinch before a beast of this level...
Pathetic. And you call yourselves my retainers?

rows.label: qst200603_0400
rows.name: That's not the point, you idiot Kubira!

rows.label: qst200603_0410
rows.name:
...This has become a mess.
What do we do, Rex?

rows.label: qst200603_0420
rows.name: What do we do...?

rows.label: qst200603_0430
rows.name: We should fall back for now.

rows.label: qst200603_0440
rows.name:
It would be better to ask the Superbian
army's Divine Beast warship for help, mo.

rows.label: qst200603_0450
rows.name: What a hopeless lot...

rows.label: qst200603_0460
rows.name: You all rest. I will defeat it.

rows.label: qst200603_0470
rows.name: ...Hold my sword.

rows.label: qst200603_0480
rows.name: You're going to die.

rows.label: qst200603_0490
rows.name:
I will not die. No, I cannot die. Not for
the sake of the people of fallen Rigideria.

rows.label: qst200603_0500
rows.name:
...Let's do it. Let's
answer Kubira's feelings.

rows.label: qst200603_0510
rows.name: Are you really sure about this, Rex?

rows.label: qst200603_0520
rows.name:
Understood. If Rex says
so, it can't be helped.

rows.label: qst200603_0530
rows.name: Let's go along with that idiot.
